{"about_the_game":"S-COPTER is a combination of an <strong>arcade game, a platformer and a bit of a puzzle game</strong>, viewed from a 2D perspective. The player\u2019s goal is to transport all the passengers on a level to their respective landing sites.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/Gif1.png?t=1668711975\" /><br><br>To complicate things a bit, there are many obstacles on the way, which, combined with limited life and fuel, force the player to carefully plan every flight.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>40 levels in single-player mode, equipped with many kinds of dangers, just waiting for one wrong move,<br></li><li>20 levels in local cooperation  mode, requiring the proper planning and coordination between two players,<br></li><li>10 maps in versus mode, in which there can be only one\u2026 surviving player,<br></li><li>difficulty so high, that you will hate us forever,<br></li><li>hand drawn 2D graphics,<br></li><li>game suitable for a five minute break at work, spontaneous beer-meetings with your friends and long sessions of cursing and throwing things.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596260/extras/Gif2.png?t=1668711975\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Get to the chopper!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/596260/2a7d2ce69adfed7763c4ed2b9aa2422272f0510a.jpg"},{"name":"Gotta catch them all!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/596260/c15aa3b7c69b343f745ae26ddafa14414ca6cb5d.jpg"},{"name":"Team effort","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/596260/08b370dfd5e4323969ea64b8bab1b00726d62caa.jpg"},{"name":"Took you long enough","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/596260/a716cace9a9233aa28156d3d8b9bdf25046e5